Processes session files to find (bot_output, teejay_response) pairs.
Classifies response type and stores as searchable preference pairs.

Usage:
    coactive extract [--force]           Extract preferences from recent sessions
    coactive search "query" [--limit N]  Search preferences by similarity
    coactive stats                       Show preference store stats
    coactive show [--type TYPE] [--limit N]  Show recent preferences
"""

